2016-04-19 Andrea Zoli <bulgarelli@iasfbo.inaf.it>
TAG v1.3.0
SphDistDeg function reworked using another more compact math solution (MathUtils.cpp).
GetRowCol function reworked, when searching for points (l, b) outside the map now the function returns false.
Changed strategy for the ellipse generation: Fix the gal and iso parameters before the contour generation.
For each step of 7 fitting steps of RoiMulti save the fitting result status or error and the cts counts being used.
Report in the output .source files the limits of flux, index, gal and iso parameters.
Report in the output .source files the TT and MJD.
Save the fluxul in the struct SourceData (used during iterative analysis).
Optimize using deltaRhoMultInv and m_fluxScaleFactorMulInv.
Changed CFLAGS. Compilation optimization flag is now -O2, added flag -pipe, etc.
Fixed warnings signed vs unsigned, char* vs const char*, unused variables, and some out-of-buffer assigments.
Inlining SphDistDeg and Sina functions (MathUtils.cpp).
Removed some memory leaks and added some null-string terminator after some strncpy calls.

